rd, and you apply the discount directly to their purchase. If you\'d like, you can load your preferred barcodes directly into Kikbak.\r\n\r\n<center>\r\n<a href=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/gift_screens_v5.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-475\" alt=\"gift_screens_v5\" src=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/gift_screens_v5.png\" width=\"468\" height=\"275\" /></a><a href=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/arrow.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-442\" alt=\"arrow\" src=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/arrow.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"84\" /></a><a href=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/hand_gift_success_v21.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-467\" alt=\"hand_gift_success_v2\" src=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/hand_gift_success_v21.gif\" width=\"263\" height=\"301\" /></a></center>[/tab]\r\n\r\n[tab title=\"You reward for successful referrals\"]We help you thank your customers for every new customer they refer. When a referred friend uses their offer, we unlock your reward for them. And redeeming a reward is just as simple as redeeming an offer.\r\n\r\n<center><a href=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/reward_screens.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-469\" alt=\"reward_screens\" src=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/reward_screens.png\" width=\"468\" height=\"275\" /></a><a href=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/arrow.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-442\" alt=\"arrow\" src=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/arrow.png\" width=\"44\" height=\"84\" /></a><a href=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/hand_credit_v4.gif\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-472\" alt=\"hand_credit_v4\" src=\"http://kikbak.me/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/hand_credit_v4.gif\" width=\"207\" height=\"297\" /></a></center>\r\n[/tab]\r\n\r\n[/tabgroup]','Your customers as your 